OL,3,CMSP makes Mother's Day call urging UK
OL,4,CGovernment to extend maternity pay
OL,6,FThe Scottish Greens are urging the UK
OL,7,FGovernment to support the next
OL,8,Fgeneration by extending maternity and
OL,9,Fpaternity pay and shared parental
OL,10,Fleave.
OL,12,FGillian Mackay MSP, who is expecting
OL,13,Fher first child this summer, marked
OL,14,FMother's Day by calling for support to
OL,15,Fbe expanded to cover 52 weeks of full
OL,16,Fpay.
