OL,3,CMSP makes Mother's Day call urging UK
OL,4,CGovernment to extend maternity pay
OL,6,F"But many are unable to do so in the
OL,7,Fway they want to and are being forced
OL,8,Fback to work early.
OL,10,F"This Mother's Day, the UK Government
OL,11,Fcould make a big difference for
OL,12,Fexpectant parents by expanding
OL,13,Fmaternity and paternity pay and
OL,14,Foffering them far greater peace of
OL,15,Fmind and stability.
OL,17,F"Statutory maternity pay in the UK is
OL,18,Ffar too low, and lags far behind many
OL,19,Fother European countries.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUyD@AOU
