OL,3,CMSP makes Mother's Day call urging UK
OL,4,CGovernment to extend maternity pay
OL,6,F"A lot of young workers, in
OL,7,Fparticular, are finding themselves
OL,8,Fsqueezed, with far too many forced to
OL,9,Fdecide against having a family or
OL,10,Fdelaying doing so for financial
OL,11,Freasons.
OL,13,F"Not everybody will want to have
OL,14,Fchildren, but people who do should not
OL,15,Fbe deterred by poor parental pay.
OL,17,F"Particularly at a time when household
OL,18,Fbills and living costs are going up,
OL,19,Fwe should be supporting parents and
OL,20,Fensuring that babies are given the
OL,21,Fbest start in life.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
