OL,3,CMSP makes Mother's Day call urging UK
OL,4,CGovernment to extend maternity pay
OL,6,F"By increasing support for parents and
OL,7,Fputting money in their pockets we can
OL,8,Fsupport our next generation and spread
OL,9,Fopportunity."
OL,11,FStatutory Maternity Pay (SMP) is paid
OL,12,Ffor up to 39 weeks at 90% of the
OL,13,Fmother's average weekly earnings
OL,14,F(before tax) for the first six weeks.
OL,16,FThis is followed by #184.03 or 90% of
OL,17,Ftheir average weekly earnings
OL,18,F(whichever is lower) for the next 33
OL,19,Fweeks.
