OL,3,CMSP makes Mother's Day call urging UK
OL,4,CGovernment to extend maternity pay
OL,6,FStatutory paternity leave is paid for
OL,7,Ftwo weeks and is either #184.03 a week
OL,8,For 90% of the person's average weekly
OL,9,Fearnings (whichever is lower).
OL,11,FShared Parental Leave allows parents
OL,12,Fto share up to 50 weeks of leave and
OL,13,Fup to 37 weeks of pay between them.
OL,15,FThe UK Government said the standard
OL,16,Frate of parental payments is reviewed
OL,17,Fannually at the discretion of the
OL,18,FSecretary of State for Work and
OL,19,FPensions.
