OL,3,CMSP makes Mother's Day call urging UK
OL,4,CGovernment to extend maternity pay
OL,6,FFrom April 2025, the rate will
OL,7,Fincrease by September 2024's Consumer
OL,8,FPrices Index (CPI) figure of 1.7%,
OL,9,Ffrom #184.03 to #187.18 per week (2025/
OL,10,F26).
OL,12,FA UK Government spokesperson said:
OL,13,F"This Government wants new mothers to
OL,14,Fbe able to take time away from work in
OL,15,Fthe later stages of their pregnancy
OL,16,Fand in the months following childbirth
OL,17,Fand are entitled to 52 weeks of leave
OL,18,Fand 39 weeks of Statutory Maternity
OL,19,FPay or Maternity Allowance.
