OL,3,CMSP makes Mother's Day call urging UK
OL,4,CGovernment to extend maternity pay
OL,6,F"Statutory Maternity Pay and Maternity
OL,7,FAllowance are uprated each year and
OL,8,Fare only one element of support
OL,9,Favailable for pregnant women and new
OL,10,Fmothers, who may also be eligible for
OL,11,FUniversal Credit or Child Benefit.
OL,13,F"As we fix the foundations of the
OL,14,Feconomy, we're uprating benefits and
OL,15,Fsupporting 700,000 of the poorest
OL,16,Ffamilies by making changes to
OL,17,FUniversal Credit deductions to help
OL,18,Flow-income households and make
OL,19,Feveryone better off."
